						               													<description>Imagine that all the main characters of &amp;quot;Inside Lapenko&amp;quot; were at your disposal.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In each round, you can become an Engineer, Shershnyaga, Igor Katamaranov and others. All characters have special properties that make them unique.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of the game is to get as many Audience Points as possible.&amp;#10;And each hero does it differently.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;While the players are making cunning plans and trying to predict the actions of their opponents in order to get ahead, a common danger looms over everyone - the Iron Sleeves organized crime group.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The bandits are hunting for the characters in order to rob them to the skin, and each rival is trying to make sure that it is you who fall into their criminal clutches.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn, face down players choose a ploy card to create difficulty for the other players. And then a character card with a unique property. Audience points are scored based on the popularity of the character played (from 0 to 5) and the ability that triggers when the card is played.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game consists of 6 rounds, in each round you play one character card. Each player has 10 character cards in their deck, which ensures good replayability.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
